# 🍽️ Berliner Küche — AI Restaurant Assistant

AI-powered restaurant chatbot for a German restaurant. 
Customers can order food, check allergens, and get 
recommendations in English and German.

## 🚀 Live Demo
[Click here to try it](your-replit-link)

## ✨ Features
- 🇩🇪 Bilingual English/German support
- 🍽️ Full menu with prices in euros
- ⚠️ Allergen information
- 🤖 AI recommendations
- 🔒 Rate limiting & input validation
- ⚡ Real-time AI responses

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
Python · Flask · Groq AI · HTML · CSS · JavaScript

## 🔒 Security
- API keys in environment variables only
- Input validation on all endpoints
- Rate limiting on chat endpoint
- Error handling for API failures

